BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:e09gB47KZH-lJGIA6nD5K
SUMMARY:Spy Maters Camp II
DTSTAMP:20260403T032250Z
DTSTART:20260413T163000Z
DESCRIPTION:Calling all young secret agents! This time kids are welcome to 
	join action-packed Outdoor Spy Camp\, where kids will train to become top-
	notch spies through thrilling challenges\, daring missions\, and teamwork!
	 Obstacle Courses & Ninja Training – Agents-in-training will test their ag
	ility\, speed\, and stealth as they navigate exciting ninja courses\, craw
	l through the forest and learn to use nature objects to complete the chall
	enge. Scavenger Hunts & Riddle Solving – Spies must sharpen their detectiv
	e skills by decoding secret messages\, solving riddles\, and uncovering hi
	dden clues to complete their top-secret missions. Nerf Battles & Tactical 
	Challenges – Gear up for friendly Nerf wars\, where teamwork and strategy 
	are key to outsmarting the opposition. Agents will also practice their pre
	cision and accuracy with target practice and stealth maneuvers. Escape Roo
	m-Style Puzzles – Secret agents will work together to crack codes\, unlock
	 treasure chests\, and solve mind-bending puzzles before time runs out! Ou
	tdoor Adventure & Camouflage Training – Spies will blend into their surrou
	ndings\, practice silent movement\, and use nature to their advantage whil
	e completing their missions. This high-energy camp is perfect for kids who
	 love adventure\, problem-solving\, and action-packed fun in the great out
	doors! Are you ready to accept the mission? - follow the link to book a sp
	ot!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/spy-maters-camp-ii/18
	306068/2026-04-13T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/spy-maters-camp-ii/183060
	68/2026-04-13T00
LOCATION:Suncatcher Forest School\, 18701 se 60th st\, Issaquah\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT6H
END:VEVENT
